{"tid":267142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【熱血公民陳柏洋刑滿獲釋】","createTime":"2017-06-02T04:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T04:55:08.000Z","uid":92301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72eaaed3e2d26bdfb544b6577352fbc37c492313","tid":267142,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T04:55:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7tn9x8sb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7tn9x8sb&h=1cc5d5f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n熱血公民柏洋於「魚蛋革命」中，因襲警及拒補罪成，被判監禁九個月。柏洋今日刑滿「放學」，一眾熱血公民及支持者到塘福迎接。<br />\n<br />\n柏洋獲釋後表示，雖然出獄後要再面對荒誕的社會，但要做的事情仍然不變，會繼續努力做該做的事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1844634975797760&amp;id=1663736447220948\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1844634975797760%26id%3D1663736447220948&d=WsXwo%2BiYvzTk4qZfM8bD7Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=49b36054\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1844634975797760&amp;id=1663736447220948</a>"}]}